Subject: [PATCH] cec: no send mute key for audio system device [1/1]

PD#SWPL-65617

Problem:
The mute state from avr could be wrong when arc
is just established.

Solution:
Init tv's volume state with unmute and don't send a
mute key to change avr's volume.

Verify:
t982_r301

Change-Id: I68db74701146529a67fb5b2c0a655210a9632b26
Signed-off-by: an.xi <an.xi@amlogic.com>
